casebody.data:
Toledo Bar Association v. Tolliver.

[Cite as Toledo Bar Assn. v. Tolliver (1992), 62 Ohio St.3d 462.]

(No. 91-1764 Submitted October 16, 1991 Decided February 5, 1992.) *463John N MacKay and J. Jeffrey Lowenstein, for relator. Lafayette E. Tolliver, pro se. Per Curiam.

We agree with the board’s findings and recommendation. Respondent is hereby publicly reprimanded. Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
